title: -Experimental study on the 3P size resonance in the P-wawe neutron strength function

x4codes.shortRef: Jour: Zeitschrift fuer Physik A, Hadrons and Nuclei, Vol.326, p.185 (1987)

x4freetext: -Experimental study on the 3P size resonance in the
Several filters. Average energy of the filtered
neutrons 143 KeV with a full half width of 20 KeV.
80 per cent of all neutrons have energies between
No explanation given for the uncertainties
Errors on parameters of strength function
include error on cross section ,on other
.The average total scattering cross sections have
been obtained from the measured total cross sections
by substracting  the nonelastic or radiative capture
cross section at 143 KeV.The best fit on the average
scattering cross section provides the P wave strength
